overview: A documentary exploring the rise and fall of 80s skateboard legend Mark "Gator" Rogowski.
original_title: Stoked: The Rise and Fall of Gator
tagline: The compelling life of Mark "Gator" Rogowski, '80s skateboarding superstar, now serving 31 years to life in prison.
cast: Mark 'Gator' Rogowski|Tony Hawk|Stacy Peralta|Steve Caballero|Jason Lee
